  "reference_number": "RUS2358",
  "remarks": "\nAnto Joseph is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on basis of the following ground: Anto Joseph is associated with a person that is or has been involved in making available funds to a person that makes available economic resources that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n",
